# CODEOWNERS — Kesher Personality Dimension
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# Rules are evaluated bottom-up; the last matching rule wins.
# Replace placeholder team/user slugs with real GitHub handles before merging.
#
# Placeholder slugs used below:
#   @org/ai-platform          — AI & platform engineers who own prompts and inference
#   @org/psychometric-research — Psychometric / research team
#   @org/privacy-legal        — Privacy & legal reviewers
#   @org/localization         — Localization / Hebrew RTL team
#   @org/ml-product           — ML / product owners (recommender, Why This Match)
#   @org/trust-safety         — Trust & Safety / moderation owners
#   @org/engineering-leads    — Engineering leads (catch-all for unowned files)

# ── Default owner (catch-all) ────────────────────────────────────────────────
*                                   @org/engineering-leads

# ── CI / GitHub configuration ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.github/                            @org/engineering-leads @org/privacy-legal

# ── AI prompts and schemas ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
src/ai/                             @org/ai-platform
src/prompts/                        @org/ai-platform
src/schemas/                        @org/ai-platform
**/*.prompt.ts                      @org/ai-platform
**/*.prompt.json                    @org/ai-platform
**/*schema*.ts                      @org/ai-platform
**/*schema*.json                    @org/ai-platform

# ── Assessment and scoring ───────────────────────────────────────────────────
src/personality/assessment/         @org/psychometric-research
src/personality/scoring/            @org/psychometric-research
src/personality/interpretation/     @org/psychometric-research @org/ai-platform
**/*scoring*                        @org/psychometric-research
**/*assessment*                     @org/psychometric-research

# ── Privacy, consent, sharing, deletion, export ─────────────────────────────
src/privacy/                        @org/privacy-legal
src/consent/                        @org/privacy-legal
src/data/                           @org/privacy-legal @org/engineering-leads
**/*consent*                        @org/privacy-legal
**/*privacy*                        @org/privacy-legal
**/*deletion*                       @org/privacy-legal
**/*export*                         @org/privacy-legal
**/*retention*                      @org/privacy-legal
firestore.rules                     @org/privacy-legal @org/engineering-leads

# ── Hebrew copy and RTL layouts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
src/i18n/                           @org/localization
src/locales/                        @org/localization
**/*.he.*                           @org/localization
**/*rtl*                            @org/localization
**/*hebrew*                         @org/localization

# ── Recommender and Why This Match ──────────────────────────────────────────
src/recommender/                    @org/ml-product
src/personality/why-this-match/     @org/ml-product @org/ai-platform
**/*recommender*                    @org/ml-product
**/*why-this-match*                 @org/ml-product

# ── Safety / moderation-adjacent features ───────────────────────────────────
src/safety/                         @org/trust-safety
src/moderation/                     @org/trust-safety
**/*safety*                         @org/trust-safety
**/*moderation*                     @org/trust-safety
**/*flagging*                       @org/trust-safety

# ── Governance docs ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
docs/personality/                   @org/privacy-legal @org/psychometric-research @org/engineering-leads
